<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='461855' id='t-461855'>about their wishes around death,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='463571' id='t-463571'>and even for people over 75,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='465505' id='t-465505'>only 45 percent of people
