<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='469464' id='t-469464'>And the reasons that
people give ... you know,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='472163' id='t-472163'>they think that their death is far off</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='474008' id='t-474008'>or they think that they're going
to make people uncomfortable</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='476909' id='t-476909'>by talking about it.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='478319' id='t-478319'>And you know, to a certain extent,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='480098' id='t-480098'>there are other people out there
