<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='483760' id='t-483760'>The government has all this regulation
and bureaucracy around things</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='487465' id='t-487465'>like burying a death, for example,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='489722' id='t-489722'>and there's people like funeral directors</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='491715' id='t-491715'>who devote their entire
