<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 8:35
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='504344' id='t-504344'>So we're not thinking about this,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='506582' id='t-506582'>but all of the people we imagine
