<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='509506' id='t-509506'>they're not taking care of it either.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 8:42
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='511575' id='t-511575'>Thank you.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 8:43
